    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine and transmission operate smoothly, and all major systems are fully functional. While the exterior shows some minor signs of age like small stone chips and light surface scratches, the paint still holds a nice shine. The interior is clean and comfortable, with only typical wear on the driver's seat bolster. It is a solid, honest car that is ready for daily use without needing immediate repairs.",
