    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m reaching out to my fellow car enthusiasts because I\u2019ve decided it\u2019s time to part with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been my 'garage queen'\u2014it\u2019s been pampered, polished, and kept in a climate-controlled environment since day one. Honestly, it looks and smells just like it did the day it left the showroom. I\u2019ve treated this car like a member of the family, and while it\u2019s hard to say goodbye, I\u2019m excited for it to go to a home where it\u2019ll be truly appreciated. It\u2019s a rare find in this kind of pristine shape, and I\u2019d love for you to come by, have a coffee, and see it for yourself!",
